Author: yes_creamcheese
Text: I shoved an entire mini KitKat in my mouth while my SO was in the bathroom brushing his teeth but then he came back to ask if I want to join him to save time. WHILE I WAS STILL CHEWING ON MY KITKAT. I looked at him with my mouth full. Seriously I couldn't even nod or shake my head to answer him because it would look weird. So I said nothing, and just... turned away??!!! Acted like I somehow didn't hear the question??!!!  Urg I am cringing at myself.
